01:03:19.328 --> 01:03:21.535
[Lady Nox] You use this monster
to welcome an ally?

01:03:24.801 --> 01:03:28.613
An ally? Do you like
my dear savage, Neon?

01:03:28.671 --> 01:03:30.878
