01:03:37.947 --> 01:03:41.485
- But it makes no sense at all.
- Sweet Aeron, I see right through you.

01:03:42.618 --> 01:03:45.258
I know your Blood Gift
is yours, and yours alone;

01:03:45.321 --> 01:03:48.165
distinct from Dark,
your Duke, and my lover.

01:03:48.224 --> 01:03:50.932
You have what is known
as Passive Evolution.

01:03:51.194 --> 01:03:55.540
When you defeat an enemy, you acquire
their power, absorbing their Blood Gift.

01:03:55.598 --> 01:03:58.579
<i>[Aaron] We arrived</i> here <i>on</i> a <i>mission--
to hunt</i> a <i>Spirit Beast.</i>

01:03:59.101 --> 01:04:01.411
<i>[Lady Nox] Ah, yes. The Spirit Beast.</i>

01:04:01.470 --> 01:04:04.314
<i>You went to that town
searching for more power--</i>

01:04:04.373 --> 01:04:06.375
<i>the power of Ice Fang.</i>

01:04:06.442 --> 01:04:08.319
<i>But you failed, didn't you?</i>

01:04:08.377 --> 01:04:10.914
<i>Dark believes you are loyal to him.</i>

01:04:11.514 --> 01:04:14.552
But your ambition
surpasses your loyalty.

01:04:14.617 --> 01:04:18.827
<i>Indeed, your ambition has surpassed
the capacity of your mortal body</i>

01:04:18.888 --> 01:04:21.391
<i>to hold all of your stolen power.</i>

01:04:21.457 --> 01:04:23.198
<i>And therein lies your problem.</i>

01:04:23.259 --> 01:04:28.004
<i>But you believe the solution is here
on Eternal island, with Hihure.</i>

01:04:28.431 --> 01:04:33.847
Once you have obtained his Blood Gift,
his power of extreme regeneration,

01:04:33.903 --> 01:04:36.281
then you will be able
to endure any attack,

01:04:36.339 --> 01:04:39.843
making you the most powerful
monster in the territory.

01:04:40.409 --> 01:04:41.410
Am I right?

01:04:42.044 --> 01:04:43.182
Or am I right?

01:04:45.948 --> 01:04:48.224
