[wind howls]

01:29:00.868 --> 01:29:02.905
[thunder rumbles]

01:29:35.203 --> 01:29:36.910
[Qrunts]

01:29:46.748 --> 01:29:50.252
Quick, Dark. We have to kill Lotus. Now.

01:29:50.318 --> 01:29:53.822
Hillure sacrificed himself to give her
the power of regeneration.

01:29:54.188 --> 01:29:55.667
That makes her Duke Six.

01:29:56.624 --> 01:29:58.467
We're running out of time.

01:29:58.726 --> 01:30:02.071
She now shares the original Soul Loop
with Duke Five.

01:30:02.130 --> 01:30:05.134
If she combines that with Hillure's
power, she can surpass anyone.

01:30:05.366 --> 01:30:07.437
Once her new Soul Loop completes

01:30:07.502 --> 01:30:10.142
there's no way any of us
will be able to stop her.

01:30:16.043 --> 01:30:18.114
[Dark hisses]

01:30:27.488 --> 01:30:29.195
[Spirit Beast chitters]

01:30:38.466 --> 01:30:42.141
[Spirit Beast coos and screeches]

01:30:43.938 --> 01:30:46.509
Dark. Zillah. Silver.

01:30:46.574 --> 01:30:48.019
Neon. Aaron.

01:30:48.075 --> 01:30:49.645
On behalf of the High Lords,

01:30:49.710 --> 01:30:52.316
I command you to get out there
and kill Lotus!

01:30:52.380 --> 01:30:54.155
We cannot let the traitor escape!

01:30:56.451 --> 01:30:57.623
[Spirit Beast caws]

01:31:08.563 --> 01:31:11.737
[ice crackles]

01:31:24.712 --> 01:31:26.191
[Spirit Beast caws]

01:31:29.817 --> 01:31:30.557
Brother!

01:31:38.192 --> 01:31:39.364
Don't kill him.

01:31:39.427 --> 01:31:41.668
<i>Don't! That's his plan!</i>

01:31:41.963 --> 01:31:44.068
She'll get his power!

01:31:44.632 --> 01:31:45.633
No, don't!

01:31:46.367 --> 01:31:48.210
-[knife punctures]
-[Dark groans]

01:31:51.005 --> 01:31:54.111
[Qfoans]

01:31:57.445 --> 01:31:59.516
<i>♪ Violin playing A'</i>

01:32:14.962 --> 01:32:16.873
<i>♪ Violin continues to play A'</i>

01:32:47.895 --> 01:32:50.569
[sobs]

01:33:07.181 --> 01:33:10.424
[Spirit Beast screeches]

01:33:10.918 --> 01:33:14.297
[moans]

01:33:14.622 --> 01:33:16.329
[screams]

01:33:17.558 --> 01:33:19.231
Look what you've done.

01:33:19.927 --> 01:33:21.770
You killed him, you idiot.

01:33:22.129 --> 01:33:23.870
His power has passed to her.

01:33:23.931 --> 01:33:28.880
She is now Duke Five and Six--
the first double-Duke in history.

01:33:40.815 --> 01:33:42.590
You killed my brother.

01:33:44.085 --> 01:33:46.691
Each one of you is to blame for this!

01:33:48.522 --> 01:33:50.058
But I'll have my vengeance.

01:33:51.726 --> 01:33:54.935
My brother may be dead,
but he will not die alone.

01:33:54.996 --> 01:33:56.669
[Spirit Beast caws]

01:33:57.164 --> 01:34:00.873
Trust me, you will accompany him!

01:34:02.303 --> 01:34:04.749
I'll make damn sure
his death wasn't in vain.

01:34:15.916 --> 01:34:18.624
[Qrunts]

01:34:18.686 --> 01:34:20.597
[screams]

01:34:22.156 --> 01:34:23.260
[Qrunts]

01:34:24.959 --> 01:34:26.233
[Spirit Beast caws]

01:34:34.435 --> 01:34:35.914
[Lady Nox] We still have a chance.

01:34:35.970 --> 01:34:38.712
The two Soul Loops haven't fused.
They're in conflict.

01:34:38.773 --> 01:34:40.309
It's our only chance to kill her.

01:34:40.374 --> 01:34:42.479
Let's go. Now!

01:34:44.612 --> 01:34:47.183
[ice crackles]

01:35:07.201 --> 01:35:09.841
[air swishes]

01:35:20.815 --> 01:35:21.987
[screams]

01:35:28.889 --> 01:35:31.233
[ice crackles]

01:35:52.246 --> 01:35:53.281
[Kira] They all left.

01:35:53.347 --> 01:35:56.123
What about you? Will you leave, too?

01:36:00.621 --> 01:36:01.463
[Asbel] I don't know.

01:36:01.956 --> 01:36:03.299
But you should go home.

01:36:04.125 --> 01:36:06.230
You parents are waiting
for you to marry.

01:36:08.763 --> 01:36:12.176
What parents?
My mother died when I was born.

01:36:12.767 --> 01:36:16.340
And my father,
I'd never seen him before today.

01:36:17.004 --> 01:36:19.883
- And now he's gone, too.
- Why is that?

01:36:19.940 --> 01:36:21.578
Duke Six. Hillure.

01:36:22.943 --> 01:36:24.115
He was my father.

01:36:25.179 --> 01:36:27.819
My mother was his Disciple.

01:36:28.249 --> 01:36:30.251
She made the ultimate sacrifice.

01:36:30.751 --> 01:36:32.162
When she was pregnant with me,

01:36:32.520 --> 01:36:34.966
I stole her Soul Loop
from within the womb.

01:36:35.790 --> 01:36:39.237
But without her,
my Soul Loop was incomplete

01:36:39.727 --> 01:36:40.728
<i>and always will be.</i>

01:36:41.228 --> 01:36:45.267
Sometimes I feel like
a lonely, deserted freak.

01:36:48.135 --> 01:36:50.137
The truth is, you're really not alone.

01:36:51.005 --> 01:36:52.916
If you're a freak, then so am I.

01:36:53.607 --> 01:36:56.645
When I was younger,
the other kids would laugh at me.

01:36:57.044 --> 01:36:58.489
I was always bullied.

01:37:00.147 --> 01:37:01.785
Then one day I met Silver,

01:37:02.116 --> 01:37:04.062
and my life was changed.

01:37:05.186 --> 01:37:06.460
It was a dream.

01:37:07.388 --> 01:37:08.526
A wonderful dream.

01:37:08.923 --> 01:37:10.402
An impossible dream.

01:37:12.293 --> 01:37:14.239
But the craziest thing about it--

01:37:14.862 --> 01:37:18.139
Now he's gone.
Like it was just a dream after all.

01:37:19.099 --> 01:37:23.241
They say a Duke and his Disciple
are like family,

01:37:23.304 --> 01:37:26.012
like lovers, but my Duke, my own father,

01:37:26.073 --> 01:37:28.952
chose to pass on his Soul Loop
to a stranger instead of me.

01:37:29.410 --> 01:37:30.582
Your Duke abandoned you.

01:37:32.313 --> 01:37:34.759
And so it seems it was all a lie.

01:37:37.952 --> 01:37:40.990
-[sniffling]
-[Asbel clears throat]

01:37:42.957 --> 01:37:44.493
Hey. Come on, cheer up.

01:37:46.493 --> 01:37:47.836
Life was hard.

01:37:49.263 --> 01:37:52.107
I was on my own, except for my parents,

01:37:53.033 --> 01:37:54.774
until Silver came along.

01:37:54.835 --> 01:37:56.109
And how he's here.

01:37:57.771 --> 01:37:59.307
He is my family now.

01:38:00.608 --> 01:38:03.748
He won't abandon me. I trust him.

01:38:06.714 --> 01:38:07.488
Hmm.

01:38:10.251 --> 01:38:13.528
I'm going back to Glanort.
I'll wait for him there.

01:38:14.255 --> 01:38:15.928
And he'll come back to me.

01:38:16.724 --> 01:38:18.260
I know he'll come back.

01:38:21.262 --> 01:38:22.536
I'll come with you.

01:38:23.297 --> 01:38:24.207
Hmm.

01:38:31.906 --> 01:38:33.817
[Qrunts]

01:38:33.874 --> 01:38:35.785
[Qfoans]

01:38:41.749 --> 01:38:44.730
I've chosen to help you,
but I need to know.

01:38:45.052 --> 01:38:46.463
What was Hillure guarding?

01:38:47.354 --> 01:38:50.858
<i>[Lotus] To answer that,
we must go back to the beginning.</i>

01:38:51.992 --> 01:38:55.030
<i>Wind Walker and I were deep
'm the Abyss Corridor.</i>

01:38:55.696 --> 01:38:59.872
<i>We were practicing our gift--
hypnotizing Spirit Beasts.</i>

01:39:00.601 --> 01:39:03.309
<i>Suddenly, he appeared.</i>

01:39:06.974 --> 01:39:09.648
Stay back! It's dangerous! You'll--

01:39:12.546 --> 01:39:14.787
[Qfoans]

01:39:20.888 --> 01:39:22.925
[grunts, groans]

01:39:29.463 --> 01:39:30.965
[metallic clang]

01:39:41.675 --> 01:39:43.951
<i>[Lotus] I thought! was helping
by warning him,</i>

01:39:44.011 --> 01:39:46.753
<i>but you might as well
tell the sun that the day is long.</i>

01:39:47.047 --> 01:39:49.527
<i>He told us his story--
we had to help him.</i>

01:39:49.950 --> 01:39:52.055
<i>So then, they hunted us.</i>

01:40:02.029 --> 01:40:04.441
Who exactly are you? Be smart, kid.

01:40:04.765 --> 01:40:06.904
I'll... show you.

01:40:14.842 --> 01:40:16.048
[laughs]

01:40:22.349 --> 01:40:23.828
[Qfoans]

01:40:24.184 --> 01:40:25.288
[screams]

01:40:25.452 --> 01:40:27.454
[Qfoans]

01:40:27.521 --> 01:40:30.331
[Qrunts]

01:40:37.398 --> 01:40:39.742
[Lady Nox] So you're saying
this boy prevented you

01:40:39.800 --> 01:40:41.643
from killing Wind Walker?

01:40:41.935 --> 01:40:46.384
[Dark] Prevented me?
It was generous of him not to kill me.

01:40:47.674 --> 01:40:50.348
If you could see no other reflection
in the mirror,

01:40:50.411 --> 01:40:53.415
surely you should have realized
that the boy's Spirit Power

01:40:53.480 --> 01:40:55.016
<i>was greater than your own.</i>

01:40:55.449 --> 01:40:57.690
<i>The Wraith Mirror showed me nothing.</i>

01:40:57.751 --> 01:40:59.822
It reflects two types of people.

01:41:00.154 --> 01:41:04.000
As you know,
those who don't have powers.

01:41:04.058 --> 01:41:07.870
And the others who the mirror reflects

01:41:07.928 --> 01:41:10.272
are those who are stronger than me.

01:41:10.330 --> 01:41:15.609
And the only one who is stronger than me
is Gilgamesh.

01:41:15.669 --> 01:41:17.205
You should have realized sooner.

01:41:18.906 --> 01:41:22.217
<i>Have you ever noticed that
'm the High Lords' temples</i>

01:41:22.276 --> 01:41:26.088
<i>only the side rooms are used
to enter their chambers?</i>

01:41:28.482 --> 01:41:31.588
<i>The door to the middle room
is always closed.</i>

01:41:31.819 --> 01:41:33.696
<i>Why do you think that is?</i>

01:41:34.922 --> 01:41:37.027
Now, I could be wrong about this,

01:41:37.491 --> 01:41:40.301
but I think the boy you met
in the Abyss Corridor

01:41:40.360 --> 01:41:43.739
is actually the High Lord
who escaped from that little room.

01:41:44.198 --> 01:41:49.546
Hmph. But the High Lords
won't leave their crystal rooms.

01:41:49.937 --> 01:41:54.977
It's not "won't"--
the truth is, they can't leave.

01:41:55.843 --> 01:42:01.418
The High Lords are powerful beings,
come to us from another world.

01:42:03.851 --> 01:42:05.956
They're confined to their quarters.

01:42:06.320 --> 01:42:10.791
We treat them as if they're gods,
but they're far from that.

01:42:13.427 --> 01:42:16.670
<i>Lotus} They're prisoners.
{Silver} What do you mean?</i>

01:42:17.164 --> 01:42:20.668
That young boy? A renegade High Lord

01:42:20.734 --> 01:42:24.807
took over his body as his own,
used it as a vessel to escape.

01:42:25.105 --> 01:42:26.880
But there was a problem.

01:42:27.574 --> 01:42:29.679
The young boy's body was still mortal.

01:42:30.344 --> 01:42:33.416
There was no way it could bear the
weight of a High Lord's soul for long.

01:42:33.947 --> 01:42:37.417
Otherwise, every single
High Lord would escape.

01:42:37.718 --> 01:42:40.221
They would leave their
crystal prisons for eternity,

01:42:40.287 --> 01:42:41.891
go out and wreak havoc.

01:42:42.322 --> 01:42:45.701
The High Lords gave orders
to hunt down my brother and I.

01:42:46.827 --> 01:42:48.864
Sounds all too familiar, doesn't it?

01:42:48.929 --> 01:42:50.704
[Lady <i>Nox] What happened
four years ago was</i>

01:42:50.764 --> 01:42:52.209
a catastrophe.

01:42:53.367 --> 01:42:55.369
The farmer, Duke One,

01:42:56.003 --> 01:42:57.448
Gilgamesh,

01:42:57.638 --> 01:42:59.083
and his Disciple

01:42:59.806 --> 01:43:01.979
were branded as traitors.

01:43:02.042 --> 01:43:06.286
And for that, we were given the task
of hunting them both down.

01:43:06.713 --> 01:43:08.659
<i>So we did just that.</i>

01:43:08.715 --> 01:43:10.160
[Teenage Boy] Gilgamesh--

01:43:10.784 --> 01:43:12.457
it wasn't him who betrayed us.

01:43:12.886 --> 01:43:15.366
He happened to know our secrets--

01:43:15.923 --> 01:43:18.995
yes, all of our secrets.

01:43:20.260 --> 01:43:25.505
He knew the reason why we're all here.
He knew our purpose.

01:43:26.600 --> 01:43:28.602
But he was too powerful for us.

01:43:29.002 --> 01:43:31.346
We were not able to destroy him.

01:43:32.172 --> 01:43:34.778
We could only trap him in a cage.

01:43:36.310 --> 01:43:38.756
So you want us to rescue Gilgamesh.

01:43:39.112 --> 01:43:41.820
No. You don't understand.

01:43:42.216 --> 01:43:46.062
Our hands were stained with blood,
stained with sin,

01:43:46.119 --> 01:43:50.033
so we were exiled and imprisoned here.

01:43:50.390 --> 01:43:53.963
But there are cracks in the prison.

01:43:54.461 --> 01:43:56.634
And the day is fast approaching

01:43:57.231 --> 01:44:00.405
when the rest of my kin
will begin to escape.

01:44:01.301 --> 01:44:05.772
And when that does happen,
this world will become another hell.

01:44:06.673 --> 01:44:09.916
And only Gilgamesh can save us all.

01:44:10.544 --> 01:44:12.455
[gasps]

01:44:12.679 --> 01:44:14.124
How do you know these secrets?

01:44:14.815 --> 01:44:18.228
Not just me.
And therein lies the danger.

01:44:18.852 --> 01:44:23.164
You see, a secret is like
a flame in the darkness

01:44:23.457 --> 01:44:24.800
with no kindling.

01:44:25.125 --> 01:44:27.605
It cannot grow into a fire.

01:44:28.562 --> 01:44:31.008
But even the smallest spark of light...

01:44:31.765 --> 01:44:32.709
[hisses]

01:44:33.900 --> 01:44:36.813
...is enough to attract predators.

01:44:38.672 --> 01:44:41.414
[Dark] I fear no one.
Where is Gilgamesh?

01:44:41.475 --> 01:44:42.852
Mm.

01:44:46.713 --> 01:44:49.887
The jail used to imprison Gilgamesh...

01:44:51.151 --> 01:44:53.256
was inside Hillure.

01:44:57.624 --> 01:44:59.763
<i>[Lady Nox] Gilgamesh discovered
that the High Lords</i>

01:44:59.826 --> 01:45:02.864
<i>are more demons than gods- as did I.</i>

01:45:03.864 --> 01:45:07.004
<i>But these demons are the ones
who give us our power.</i>

01:45:07.334 --> 01:45:11.840
<i>Unlike that fool Gilgamesh,
1 refuse to bite the hand that feeds us.</i>

01:45:12.406 --> 01:45:16.354
<i>Because of his strength, the High Lords
had to find somewhere to jail him</i>

01:45:16.877 --> 01:45:19.448
<i>from which it was impossible to escape.</i>

01:45:19.746 --> 01:45:22.625
<i>Hillure's blood gift
of eternal regeneration</i>

01:45:22.683 --> 01:45:24.253
<i>let him merge with the island</i>

01:45:24.318 --> 01:45:27.527
<i>and kept Gilgamesh 's
imprisonment eternal.</i>

01:45:28.021 --> 01:45:30.968
<i>[Dark] So Hiﬂure sacrificed himself,</i>

01:45:31.358 --> 01:45:35.170
and then made Lotus
the new immortal Duke.

01:45:36.563 --> 01:45:39.271
Because he wanted to release Gilgamesh?

01:45:39.333 --> 01:45:40.937
Possibly.

01:45:43.236 --> 01:45:46.080
Or maybe.

01:45:46.540 --> 01:45:48.520
<i>Just maybe,</i>

01:45:48.809 --> 01:45:51.085
<i>he was tired of eternity,</i>

01:45:52.212 --> 01:45:54.715
<i>living in a state of limbo.</i>

01:45:57.751 --> 01:46:01.631
<i>No one wants to be half-dead forever.</i>

01:46:23.276 --> 01:46:24.778
So much secrecy.

01:46:26.046 --> 01:46:28.526
I wonder how many lies
are in this kingdom?

01:46:28.982 --> 01:46:31.553
More than you can ever imagine.

01:46:33.353 --> 01:46:35.060
<i>I will</i> tell you more,

01:46:35.756 --> 01:46:39.101
however, first you must promise me

01:46:39.893 --> 01:46:42.373
that you will stand by my side.

01:46:45.465 --> 01:46:47.240
And what side is that?

01:46:49.803 --> 01:46:51.805
The side that will survive...

01:46:53.073 --> 01:46:54.677
of course.

01:46:54.741 --> 01:46:57.381
[moans]

01:46:57.978 --> 01:47:00.151
[laughs softly]

01:47:04.351 --> 01:47:07.127
[Lotus] I wanted to be a Duke so badly,

01:47:07.454 --> 01:47:10.128
to always remain loyal
to the High Lords.

01:47:12.526 --> 01:47:14.528
I wanted to guard Ashland with my life.

01:47:14.961 --> 01:47:17.874
But it turns out the Dukes
are just ignorant pawns.

01:47:18.965 --> 01:47:20.842
Doing whatever the High Lords want.

01:47:24.371 --> 01:47:27.147
And at the end of the day,
we're disposable.

01:47:27.607 --> 01:47:30.884
We're practically Spirit Beasts
residing in human form.

01:47:31.545 --> 01:47:33.286
No more and no less.

01:47:33.613 --> 01:47:35.650
I've had to learn to accept that.

01:47:36.750 --> 01:47:38.457
It's not easy.

01:47:39.286 --> 01:47:43.666
Long ago, the world was filled
with a great number of Dukes--

01:47:44.157 --> 01:47:45.500
<i>new Dukes were born,</i>

01:47:46.393 --> 01:47:47.838
<i>old Dukes died.</i>

01:47:48.395 --> 01:47:51.865
<i>The fortunes of noble families
rose and fell accordingly.</i>

01:47:51.932 --> 01:47:55.277
<i>Eventually, legends
were turned into relics.</i>

01:47:55.335 --> 01:47:58.282
<i>Their secrets were shrouded in darkness.</i>

01:47:59.239 --> 01:48:02.118
<i>Since the dawn of time,
people have killed</i>

01:48:03.543 --> 01:48:04.715
<i>in pursuit of glory...</i>

01:48:05.846 --> 01:48:06.790
<i>wealth...</i>

01:48:07.814 --> 01:48:10.693
<i>Power... and justice.</i>

01:48:10.750 --> 01:48:13.230
<i>Yet they all end up in the same place:</i>

01:48:13.286 --> 01:48:14.560
<i>destruction.</i>

01:48:15.522 --> 01:48:18.332
<i>They wanted to hoard their Spirit Power</i>

01:48:18.391 --> 01:48:21.838
<i>and allow their descendants
to worship them as legends.</i>

01:48:22.929 --> 01:48:26.172
<i>Instead, they became cold skeletons,</i>

01:48:27.100 --> 01:48:29.637
<i>their emotions withering away</i>

01:48:29.870 --> 01:48:31.508
<i>until they perished.</i>

01:48:33.940 --> 01:48:35.647
<i>Nothing was left inside them</i>

01:48:35.709 --> 01:48:39.213
<i>but an insatiable desire
for even more Spirit Power--</i>

01:48:39.412 --> 01:48:44.088
<i>a dark, soulless ambition
that filIs this world with blealmess.</i>

01:48:50.123 --> 01:48:52.296
So, then, are you going
to help me practice?

01:48:57.063 --> 01:48:59.407
[soft whooshing]

01:49:06.640 --> 01:49:09.746
<i>[Lotus] When 1 found out
about all this, it was a burden.</i>

01:49:10.677 --> 01:49:11.917
It was hard to cope.

01:49:13.914 --> 01:49:14.949
Not now.

01:49:15.515 --> 01:49:18.325
Now there's only one thing
left for me to feel.

01:49:18.385 --> 01:49:20.524
- Sorrow?
- Anger.

01:49:21.021 --> 01:49:22.466
Now tell me...

01:49:27.994 --> 01:49:31.271
Ever since the catastrophe
first happened four years ago,

01:49:31.331 --> 01:49:33.140
you've kept a low profile.

01:49:34.434 --> 01:49:36.778
You've maintained a dignified silence,

01:49:37.237 --> 01:49:40.707
you've kept away from the fight
for power and control.

01:49:40.941 --> 01:49:43.251
What I wouldn't give to see Gilgamesh.

01:49:43.543 --> 01:49:44.749
[thunder crackles]

01:49:47.647 --> 01:49:49.524
I was his Disciple then.

01:49:51.518 --> 01:49:55.898
And so... my heart
still remains with him.

01:49:57.524 --> 01:49:59.003
What about Asbel?

01:50:23.416 --> 01:50:24.827
Ahh.

01:50:31.658 --> 01:50:33.262
- Hmm.
- Huh.

01:50:36.062 --> 01:50:37.700
Asbel, don't worry.

01:50:38.898 --> 01:50:41.845
I'll return... eventually.

01:50:48.141 --> 01:50:49.882
[gasp]

01:51:29.516 --> 01:51:32.963
<i>[Silver] To save Gilgamesh,
we must overcome many hurdles.</i>

01:51:33.386 --> 01:51:36.731
<i>We will become enemies of all the Dukes
and of their Disciples.</i>

01:51:37.090 --> 01:51:38.592
<i>Danger lies ahead.</i>

01:51:39.159 --> 01:51:41.002
<i>But there is hope 'm the darkness-</i>

01:51:41.194 --> 01:51:44.664
<i>a pinprick, yet bright enough
to follow, and believe in.</i>

01:51:45.365 --> 01:51:48.209
<i>Gilgamesh, I will see you again.</i>

01:51:48.768 --> 01:51:50.509
<i>Your prison is no longer eternal.</i>

01:51:51.705 --> 01:51:54.549
<i>You will awaken, and you will save us.</i>

01:52:02.148 --> 01:52:04.355
[thunder rumbles]

